comments: Williams III (BOS) makes contact with the ball first, but then makes contact with Harris's (DEN) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Harris (DEN) briefly grasps Smart (BOS) off ball before releasing.
Jokic (DEN) sets the pick in Smart's (BOS) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Tatum (BOS) gathers on his left foot and takes two steps before shooting.
Williams III (BOS) makes marginal contact with Barton (DEN) as he disengages from the pick.
Tatum (BOS) makes marginal contact with Murray's (DEN) body during his shooting motion on his driving shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) sets the pick in Wanamaker's (BOS) path and absorbs the contact.
Smart (BOS) gathers the ball on both feet, then moves both of his feet before releasing his dribble.
Jokic (DEN) sets the pick in Wanamaker's (BOS) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Harris (DEN) makes marginal contact with Tatum (BOS) off ball and does not affect his ability to maintain his position.
Murray (DEN) makes marginal contact with Brown (BOS) that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
Smart (BOS) commits a take foul on Harris (DEN).
Tatum (BOS) briefly engages with Murray (DEN) before releasing.
Tatum (BOS) and Barton (DEN) engage and separate during the inbound.
Wanamaker (BOS) briefly grasps Murray (DEN) before releasing during the inbound.
Wanamaker (BOS) commits a take foul on Murray (DEN).
